---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Subscription Terms | Leben in Deutschland">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Subscription Terms</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-blue max-w-none space-y-6 text-gray-700">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">1. Subscription Plans</h2>
        <p>We offer auto-renewing subscription plans that may include monthly or annual options ("Premium Access").</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2. Free Trial</h2>
        <p>Your subscription may start with a free trial. The duration of the trial period is specified at sign-up. If you do not cancel before the trial ends, you will be charged the subscription fee.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">3. Billing and Cancellation</h2>
        <p>Subscriptions renew automatically unless disabled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage and cancel your subscriptions in your App Store or Google Play account settings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">4. Refunds</h2>
        <p>Refund requests are handled directly by the respective app store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) according to their refund policies.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">5. Changes to Pricing</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to change our subscription plans or adjust pricing for our service in any manner and at any time as we may determine in our sole and absolute discretion.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 font-medium">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
